{"word":"Treaty","slug":"treaty","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Treaty</b> Between nations:<br/> - Israelites and Gibeonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=15'>Jos 9:15</a> <br/> - Judah and Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ki 15:19</a> <br/> Cession of territory by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=9&verse=14'>1Ki 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=34'>1Ki 20:34</a><br/> Sacredness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=21'>Jos 9:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=2&verse=21'>Jos 2:21</a><br/> Reciprocity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=12'>1Ki 5:12</a><br/> With idolatrous nations forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=12'>Exo 34:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=15'>Exo 34:15</a>"}]}